<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1037832" n="6v"/>
    <opener><salute><lb/>Amico suo charissimo <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-140736662">Fr. C.</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">N. B.</rs></salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Ne te qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so male habeat, amice optime, quod tam lentus sim in scribendo, hactenus
<lb/>enim dum ruri fuimus nulla co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>oda se mihi obtulit ad vos scribendi occasio, nunc autem in <rs type="place">Urbem</rs>
<lb/>rediens nihil negotii mihi suscipiendum esse reor priusquam me debito, quod nuperrim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
<lb/>tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="letter">liter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> mihi contraxerunt, exsolverim, aut saltem impossibilitatem me eo unquam
<lb/>liberandi tibi demonstraverim; siquidem valde metuo, ne tuus in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ternum maneam debi<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tor, ita enim me affecerunt <rs type="letter">liter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> plen<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> amoris et solatii, ut quid ad eas respon<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>deam nesciam; hoc unum mihi superesse video, ut tibi pro sincero quo me proseque<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>ris affectu, et cujus tam luculenta mihi omni tempore exhibuisti testimonia, debitas
<lb/>gratias agam, mihique gratuler, quod in te solo nactus sim verum amicum; beabis
<lb/>me su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>opere, si me quoque pro tali habeas, nec dubites, me eodem semper erga te
<lb/>animo fuisse et in posterum fore. Admonitionibus tuis saluberrimis quantum
<pb facs="1037833" n="7r"/>
fieri potest obtemperare, et id quod officii mei esse putas diligenter explere studebo; propterea
<lb/>ex his regionibus quamprimum discedere in animo habeo, et quidem <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>si Deus volet<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> vel sta<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tim post <date>Paschatis</date> festum, quo tempore co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>oda <add>erit</add> occasio <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basileam</rs> revertendi cum
<lb/><rs type="person">mercatoribus</rs> nostratibus ad nundinas proxime instantes venturis; vel i<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ediate post adven<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tum <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-123503094">Nic. Schwartzii</rs>, cujus equum, si quo vehetur, domum reducere potero. Doleo
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1132220874">Jer. Raillardum</rs> per <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661552">Bernam</rs> iter non fecisse, ejus gratia per integrum diem solus in
    <lb/><rs type="place">Urbe</rs> mansi. <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-116082356">Battierio</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>quem, si placet, meo nomine iterum salutabis<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661552">Bernen<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>ses</rs> Professionem Juridicam offerre volunt, sed quo cum successu ipse iudicare poteris.
<lb/>Valde scire laboro, an Magistratus Politicus sententiam tulerit in causa appellationis
<lb/>Rh<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>torum contra <rs type="person">heredes</rs> <rs type="person">Tonjol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>, et quid Magnates nostri sua contra hanc appella<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tionem protestatione effecerint; c<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum an <rs type="organisation">Academia</rs> nostra privilegio de non ap<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>pellando munita sit ignoro, si tamen <rs type="organisation">Academi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Bononiensis</rs> et <rs type="organisation"><unclear reason="illegible">Pataviensis</unclear></rs><note type="editorial">Das schwer lesbare Wort Pataviensis wurde durchgestrichen. Unklar, wie diese Korrektur gemeint ist, da der Satz sonst nicht aufgeht.</note>, in quar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
<lb/>exemplum <rs type="organisation">nostra</rs> instituta est, hoc privilegio gaudeant, <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quum est, ut Magistratus
<lb/><rs type="organisation">nostram</rs> eodem jure uti sinat. <rs type="person">Grundlerus</rs> <rs type="biblio">dissertationem</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> se factam procul dubio
<lb/>jam publice defendit, sin minus, spero me ejus <rs type="biblio">Disputationi</rs> interfuturum. Sed quid
<lb/>agit <abbr>D<supplied>.</supplied></abbr> <rs type="person">...</rs> nomen ejus non exprimo, scis enim quem volo, valeat ille cum moribus
<lb/>suis probatissimis.</p> <closer>Tu autem, mi amice, bene vale, et quanto brevior est epistola
    <lb/>h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c, tanto prolixiorem esse meum in te affectum cogita. <dateline><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661552">Bern<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1710-04-05">5. <abbr>Apr.</abbr> 1710.</date></dateline></closer>
</div>
